Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
report_noise_lib_pin(25.10)                        report_noise_lib_pin(25.10)

Name
       report_noise_lib_pin  - Generates a report providing information on all
       the user-specified noise mappings in the design

Syntax
       report_noise_lib_pin

       [-help]

       [> <filename>]

       Generates a report providing  information  on  all  the  user-specified
       noise mappings in the design.

Parameters
       -help  Prints out the command usage.

       > <filename>
              Writes  the  report  to the specified file name. If the file al-
              ready exists, the software will overwrite it.

Examples
              * The following command generates the output report  `noise_map-
                ping.rpt' which contains all the noise mappings present in the
                design:

                report_noise_lib_pin > noise_mapping.rpt

                noise_mapping.rpt

                ---------------------------------------------------

                from_pin                    to_pin

                ---------------------------------------------------

                library1/inverter/I         library2/macro/A

                library1/buffer/I           library3/memory/ADD[0]

                ---------------------------------------------------

Related Information
              * set_noise_lib_pin

              * reset_noise_lib_pin

